00:00:11.143 --> 00:00:13.379
NARRATOR: Is this coffee?

00:00:13.412 --> 00:00:16.149
Why, no.

00:00:16.182 --> 00:00:18.418
This is coffee.

00:00:18.451 --> 00:00:28.495
[music playing]

00:00:28.495 --> 00:00:33.566
[music playing]

00:00:33.599 --> 00:00:36.135
NARRATOR: The taste
of fine coffee

00:00:36.168 --> 00:00:38.638
extend over a wide range.

00:00:38.671 --> 00:00:44.410
But for each palate, there is
a flavor that is just right.

00:00:44.443 --> 00:00:46.579
Around the world, they
drink this beverage

00:00:46.612 --> 00:00:49.582
in it's many exotic forms.

00:00:49.615 --> 00:00:54.854
How then do we make a perfect
cup of coffee to our taste?

00:00:54.887 --> 00:00:58.458
Success lies in a single word--

00:00:58.491 --> 00:01:00.326
care.

00:01:00.359 --> 00:01:03.863
Three simple ingredients go
into the brewing process--

00:01:03.896 --> 00:01:10.336
water, fresh and
carefully measured,

00:01:10.369 --> 00:01:18.578
coffee, the proper grind,
and carefully measured, time,

00:01:18.611 --> 00:01:19.479
carefully measured.

00:01:23.315 --> 00:01:27.753
A simple recipe
for perfect coffee.

00:01:27.786 --> 00:01:30.556
Perfect coffee.

00:01:30.589 --> 00:01:34.861
It helps to start the day
with warmth and vigor.

00:01:34.894 --> 00:01:44.303
[music playing]

00:01:44.336 --> 00:01:46.406
NARRATOR: It is a pleasant
splurge of the mornings work.

00:01:52.778 --> 00:01:56.649
It provides the essential
part of our pause at noon,

00:01:56.682 --> 00:02:00.253
indispensable during that
unhurried hour in a world

00:02:00.286 --> 00:02:01.688
that often forgets to stop.

00:02:05.524 --> 00:02:10.329
In the romance of evening
when young dreams glow softly,

00:02:10.362 --> 00:02:14.400
coffee is always a
perfect companion.

00:02:14.433 --> 00:02:18.204
And after dinner, it is
at home in any setting

00:02:18.237 --> 00:02:20.873
when good taste is important.

00:02:20.906 --> 00:02:26.245
In the end, it remains a
simple thing, easy to attain,

00:02:26.278 --> 00:02:30.283
well made and well enjoyed.

00:02:30.316 --> 00:02:33.319
A good cup of good coffee.

